UX Rules:
- Use tables with search, filters, sorting, and pagination.
- Every detail page should have breadcrumbs.
- Use status chips:
  - online
  - offline
  - error
  - open
  - closed
  - active
  - inactive
  - failed
  - acknowledged
  - pending
- Use confirmation modal before destructive or device actions.
- Device actions like open/close valve must show clear warning.
- Disable command action if masterController is disabled.
- Show warning if masterController is offline:
  "Master controller is offline. Command may be queued and expire later."
- Show failedReason wherever available.
- Keep admin actions auditable in UI placeholders.

